[Fringe Weaver: Increases damage by 35% to all allies for 5 seconds, After initial buff expires, echelon receives a -15% damage and accuracy penalty for 3 seconds.],
[Sugar Rush: Increases damage by 18% to all allies for 8 seconds.]

name: Sei
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Moonblast]: Shield's HP scaling is doubled.
[Active]: Grants a shield with 32 HP to all allied SG's, SMG's and HG's. The lower the HP of the ally, the higher the HP of the shield, ranging from 0.8x to 1.8x of the base value. Lasts for 5 seconds.
[Passive]: When Stella is present, Sei's attacks will be counted towards Stella's passive.

name: Dorothy
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Piano Women]: Reduce the negative effects of her skill by 50%.
[Passive]: Dorothy will use Nano-camouflage by default if she is in the middle row, otherwise she will use MIRD113.
[Active]: Toggles between one of two skill effects;
[MIRD113: Increases damage by 100% but reduces the accuracy of allies in the same column by 40% and increases their evasion by 80%.],
[Nano-camouflage: Increases evasion by 100% but reduces the evasion of allies in the same column by 40% and increases their accuracy by 80%.]

name: Stella
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Bleeding Jane]: Puppets only require 10 attacks to activate her passive.
[Active]: Increases damage by 50% for 5 seconds.
[Passive 1]: When her puppets attack over 16 times, their next round of attacks does +50% critical damage.
[Passive 2]: When Sei is present, provide 10% reduction to her skill's base cooldown (Does not affect her initial cooldown).

name: Alma
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Brantini]: Increase the duration of the drones by 1 second.
[Active]: Summons 2 additional drones to attack alongside her. The additional drones will deal 40% damage each and lasts for 4 seconds.

name: Dana
skill_desc:
[Favorite Drink - Big Beer] - Gains a 0.5 HP shield for every 1 point of armor Dana has.
[Passive]: Fires an exploding rocket fist. Can only attack 1 enemy, dealing 1.8x damage and has 10% chance of knockback (Does not stack with Slugs).
[Active]: Jumps up and smashes the ground, causing a large explosion dealing 0.6x damage and knockback to enemies within a radius of 2 units. Increases the damage of the skill by 1% for every 1 point of armor Dana has.
